<wfauthor>By Sameer Bhatnagar</wfauthor>
<wfdescription>&lt;p&gt;In this single-class activity, students sort physics problems into categories of their own choosing based on the underlying physics rather than on superficial qualities and provide a written rationale for the choices. Students learn to analyze problems and identify key features at a deeper level. See a full description &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.saltise.ca/activity/problem-sorting-review/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</wfdescription>
