<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;Perform a &lt;a href="https://www.saltise.ca/strategy/gallery-walk/" target="_blank"&gt;Gallery Walk&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Move from one workstation to the next to review and discuss each other's work.&lt;/p&gt;</textHTML>
